+ Community protection and justice administration services e.g. police stations, fire stations, coastguard and life boat stations, and law courts.

+ Community protection and detention centres e.g. borstals, prisons, remand homes.

+ Community meeting places e.g. community centre, public hall, church hall, youth club.

+ Public sanitation facilities e.g. public baths and conveniences.

+ Animal welfare facilities e.g. animal treatment, veterinary surgery, animal quarantining, cattery, kennel
